schools.name: J. M. Tate Senior High School

data.description: Welcome home! This 4BR/3BA home has been meticulously maintained and is ready for a new owner! This one has it all! The massive kitchen is a must-see with the exquisite stonework and open concept feel! Tons of storage! The backyard is huge and private! Awesome covered open patio perfect for entertaining guests! Master bedroom has two large walk-in closets and very spacious bathroom. Completely repainted interior, hardwood floors, fantastic flex room, and garage with peg board and cabinets. Milestone offers a beautiful park, paved walking trails, basketball court, playground, picnic and gazebo area. Easy access to shopping, dining, and the interstate! This one won't last long! A must see!
